he public  except the Superintendent s Reception    What should I wear   Answer Casual business attire is appropriate for all events    Are there public restrooms  Answer Restrooms are located in J M  Hall  Preston Library  Cameron Hall and Lejeune Hall located at the end of Third Barracks  Where do I order Announcements   Invitations  Personalized commencement announcements may be ordered from Herff Jones www herffjones com  Where do I order graduation photos  Graduation photos can be purchased from Candid Color Photography approximately ten days after graduation  Please visit their website at www candidcolor net  You may also call 1 800 321 4256  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 